#: cymel.core.cyobjects.objectref.ObjectRef:1 of
msgid "`.CyObject` の参照が切れていても再取得が可能な弱参照ラッパー。"
msgstr ""
"A weak reference wrapper that allows you to re-obtain the reference to "
"`.CyObject` even if it is lost."

#: cymel.core.cyobjects.objectref.ObjectRef:3 of
msgid "これ自身も `.CyObject` であるため、参照先を得ずとも、 基底でサポートする範囲でオリジナルのようにも振る舞える。"
msgstr ""
"Since this itself is also `.CyObject`, it can behave like the original as "
"long as it is supported by the base without obtaining a reference."

